{\"ngram\": \"security gaps\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There has been no immediate claim of responsibility, and Prime Minister Gabriel Attal stressed that it was too early to speculate about who might be behind them.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Attal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no immediate claim\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What we know, what we see, is that this operation was prepared, coordinated, that nerve centres were targeted, which shows a certain knowledge of the network to know where to strike,' he said.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this operation\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"nerve centres\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain knowledge\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"the network\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutor's office said that an investigation would be overseen by its organised crime office, with the anti-terrorist sub-directorate (SDAT), a branch of the judicial police that typically monitors far-left, far-right and radical environmental groups, coordinating investigations.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.859663041411362e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/